<L>__{exterior cairo docks night}
<A>__{the waterfront is dark and misty. an old tramp steamer, the bantu wind, sits by the pier. several fierce black african pirates, the crewmembers, are taking on final stores. a small light illuminates the top of the gangplank. in its circle, indy and marion exchange long, warm embraces with sallah. a short distance away the ship's captain, a handsome, powerful black named simon katanga, watches from the rail, smoking a pipe.}
